\c 7 Kunyengedzera kwechifeve 71 Mwanakomana wangu, chengeta mashoko angu, Viga mirairo yangu kwauri. 2 Chengeta mirairo yangu, urarame; Nomurau wangu semboni yeziso rako. 3 Uzvisungire paminwe yako; Uzvinyore pahwendefa romwoyo wako. 4 Uti kuuchenjeri, "Ndiwe hanzvadzi yangu; Utumidze njere shamwari yako;" 5 Kuti zvikuchengete pamukadzi wokumwe, Pamutorwa anobata kumeso namashoko ake. 6 Nokuti ndakatarira pawindo yeimba yangu, Pahutanda hwewindo yangu; 7 Ndikatarira pakati pavasina mano, Ndikaona pakati pamajaya Rimwe jaya rakashaiwa njere; 8 Richipfuura nenzira yomumusha pedyo nekona yeimba yomukadzi
